latestIgtvVideos.title: Outfit Check: @swapnationuk
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
•
•
Finally back with another #OutfitCheck and it’s all about #swapnation the first physical fashion swap shop store in London. Based in #Shoreditch you can swap items you no longer wearing for preloved items from a community of like minded shoppers! It’s a great way to get more from the clothing we buy and do your bit for the environment at the same time! Win win 🏆 
•
•
Give them a follow @swapnationuk to find out exactly how it works and start swapping! 
•
•
